Question: Locate all lines containing 'FATAL' in the payment gateway log.
Call: { "func_call": "grep_file", "pattern": "FATAL", "path": "/var/log/payments/gateway.log", "flags": "" }
Response: { "matches": [{ "file": "/var/log/payments/gateway.log", "line": 156, "text": "2023-11-05 14:22:10 FATAL Transaction ID 9982 failed verification" }, { "file": "/var/log/payments/gateway.log", "line": 189, "text": "2023-11-05 14:25:33 FATAL Service unreachable" }], "count": 2 }

